elements.title: Catherine, Princess of Wales
elements.contents: ... that Catherine, Princess of Wales (pictured), is a keen amateur photographer and the patron of the Royal Photographic Society, and has taken many official photographs of her children?

elements.title: a Connecticut radio station
elements.contents: ... that a Connecticut radio station left the FM band for good after it was out of service for a week and only one person wrote a letter to complain?
